<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Gestión de Eventos</title>
    <link href="./view//bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script type="text/javascript" src="./view/jquery/jquery-3.3.1.min.js" rel="script"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="./view/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.js" rel="script"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.6.1/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-gfdkjb5BdAXd+lj+gudLWI+BXq4IuLW5IT+brZEZsLFm++aCMlF1V92rMkPaX4PP" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
{% block navbar %}
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="./index.php">App locales Eventos</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-controls="navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
            <div class="navbar-nav">
                {% block navbarNavigation %}{% endblock %}
            </div>
        </div>
        {% block busqueda %}
            <form id="busqueda" class="form-inline needs-validation" novalidate>
                <input id="busquedaInput" class="form-control mr-sm-2" type="search" placeholder="Búsqueda de eventos" aria-label="Buscar" required>
                <li class="btn btn-outline-success my-2 my-sm-0 dropdown">
                    <span class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Buscar por</span>
                    <div class="dropdown-menu">
                        <span id="busquedaTipo" class="dropdown-item">Tipo</span>
                        <span id="busquedaLocal" class="dropdown-item">Local</span>
                        <span id="busquedaFecha" class="dropdown-item">Fecha</span>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </form>
        {% endblock %}
    </nav>
{% endblock %}
<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row col-md-12 justify-content-center">
        <h1>Gestion de Eventos</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="row col-md-12 justify-content-center">
        <p>Este proyecto muestra cómo hacer una aplicación web MVC con PHP.</p>
        <p>El objectivo es mostrar cómo realizar una aplicación utilizando éste patrón de diseño</p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            {% block cuerpo %}{% endblock %}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% block script %}{% endblock %}
</body>
</html>